data.text:
Community features

Welcome to Valley View, a unique manufactured home community designed for the convenience of our residents. Our experienced and professional management staff handles the day-to-day responsibilities of the community, so you can enjoy the beautifully landscaped grounds and contemporary amenities planned with your family in mind. Located just 21 miles from Rochester, our community sits inside of a great school district. Around your home, there are many things to do such as shopping at Walmart, Sunshine Food, and Hardware Hank, as well as dining out at favorite local restaurants like Plaza Morena Campestre Grill and Pure Country Family Dining. Nearby, there are fun activities and attractions such as Oxbow Park & Zollman Zoo, Riverside Park, and Zumbro Valley Golf Course for friends and family to enjoy. Also bring your furry family members with you because we are a pet-friendly community. Let us help you make your dream of home ownership a reality within our community!
